  "explicit_conflicts": [],
  "focus_spans": [
    {
      "end_byte": 94,
      "focus_id": "F001",
      "source_text": "五个问题不是孤立求值，而是沿着",
      "source_text_sha256": "c862d5cecb20734b75b41abcb50a466302fd1b2dbdad54602a49c464c4cbb144",
      "start_byte": 49
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 517,
      "focus_id": "F002",
      "source_text": "问题一并不是简单比较禁渔前后的数量涨跌，而是要说明",
      "source_text_sha256": "136d5ec6e3de73316ab38701cfb4d89564c73e0666cd2f14e86a184487e1b4c3",
      "start_byte": 442
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 1003,
      "focus_id": "F003",
      "source_text": "更具体地说，",
      "source_text_sha256": "6e181abd3d2eade87bc048feb58dd9c0179d72baf33c4c8559788bc95a38caab",
      "start_byte": 985
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 1683,
      "focus_id": "F004",
      "source_text": "从解释口径上看，这一问更适合按阶段来读：",
      "source_text_sha256": "914724ad0e48e1096d26ad38f6e0228d9af3a2c5822146dec756b6f0f980772b",
      "start_byte": 1623
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 2115,
      "focus_id": "F005",
      "source_text": "这样的分析",
      "source_text_sha256": "c5020ddbef4c629c5029397f51b6a19a11c3e9219a10dc6d077f7922a9b7c303",
      "start_byte": 2100
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 2261,
      "focus_id": "F006",
      "source_text": "因此，后文若出现",
      "source_text_sha256": "408e4e953f4d3d0cc9abb6546eceb20d99d062f16137844fb77e32db35b852c6",
      "start_byte": 2237
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 3743,
      "focus_id": "F007",
      "source_text": "只有把这些事实放进统一框架，才能说明禁渔收益是如何在食物网和生境连通性上被放大或削弱的，也才能解释为什么同处一个背景下，江豚和长江鲟会表现出不同的恢复曲线",
      "source_text_sha256": "349059a33fb428163f535a074f58c263e90262a9ce0d4394fce85448b792447f",
      "start_byte": 3512
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 4493,
      "focus_id": "F008",
      "source_text": "表格的作用也在于让读者一眼看出每个参数到底来自哪条事实链，而不是把变量当成纯数学符号使用。",
      "source_text_sha256": "e3ed1f26c00f0dfea22a632baa73a942dad818547b988eafd6de1fe790b0d99b",
      "start_byte": 4358
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 4661,
      "focus_id": "F009",
      "source_text": "这样写，问题二的证据链就会更完整：上游是禁渔和食源恢复，中间是通道、放流与污染修正，下游才是珍稀物种的数量变化。",
      "source_text_sha256": "12946cebd2abf09311595cc644ccf69aee0f53392a07f5ee8cd12ea1fc67282c",
      "start_byte": 4493
    }
  ],
